The,Infinispan,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,distributed,in,memory,key,value,data,storage,into,their,projects,and,applications,The,API,offers,advanced,functionality,such,as,transactions,events,querying,and,distributed,processing,Infinispan,is,an,open,source,platform,written,in,Java,It,usually,serves,as,a,distributed,cache,but,can,also,be,used,as,a,NoSQL,key,value,store,or,object,database